message.content: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL. The paper describes a SemEval task focused on extracting keyphrases and relations from scientific documents, which involves natural language processing, information retrieval, machine learning, and deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DL (Machine Learning and Deep Learning).
